<text top="55" left="90" width="103" height="14" font="1">Security Council</text>
<text top="55" left="730" width="98" height="14" font="1">3622nd meeting</text>
<text top="73" left="90" width="89" height="14" font="1">Fifty-first year</text>
<text top="73" left="726" width="102" height="14" font="1">29 January 1996</text>
<text top="109" left="90" width="358" height="14" font="1">the Secretary-General and his staff in this regard and</text>
<text top="127" left="90" width="65" height="14" font="1">commends</text>
<text top="127" left="171" width="60" height="14" font="1">UNIFIL's</text>
<text top="127" left="247" width="38" height="14" font="1">troops</text>
<text top="127" left="301" width="22" height="14" font="1">and</text>
<text top="127" left="338" width="110" height="14" font="1">troop-contributing</text>
<text top="145" left="90" width="358" height="14" font="1">countries for their sacrifices and commitment to the cause</text>
<text top="163" left="90" width="12" height="14" font="1">of</text>
<text top="163" left="117" width="76" height="14" font="1">international</text>
<text top="163" left="206" width="34" height="14" font="1">peace</text>
<text top="163" left="255" width="22" height="14" font="1">and</text>
<text top="163" left="290" width="47" height="14" font="1">security</text>
<text top="163" left="352" width="34" height="14" font="1">under</text>
<text top="163" left="400" width="48" height="14" font="1">difficult</text>
<text top="181" left="90" width="95" height="14" font="1">circumstances."</text>
<text top="217" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">This statement will be issued as a document of the</text>
<text top="235" left="90" width="317" height="14" font="1">Security Council under the symbol S/PRST/1996/5.</text>
<text top="109" left="512" width="316" height="14" font="1">The Security Council has thus concluded the present</text>
<text top="127" left="481" width="321" height="14" font="1">stage of its consideration of the item on the agenda.</text>
<text top="164" left="512" width="185" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 3.55 p.m.</i></text>
<text top="1084" left="821" width="8" height="14" font="1">3</text>
</page>
